# Sound Effects Directory

This directory contains sound effect files for the D&D Campaign Manager.

## Required Sound Files

Place the following MP3 files in this directory:

- dice-roll.mp3 - General dice roll sound
- dice-crit-success.mp3 - Critical success (nat 20) sound
- dice-crit-fail.mp3 - Critical failure (nat 1) sound
- initiative-start.mp3 - Combat/initiative start sound
- initiative-next.mp3 - Turn change sound
- combatant-added.mp3 - New combatant added sound
- ability-cast.mp3 - Ability/spell cast sound
- marker-placed.mp3 - Map marker placement sound
- marker-removed.mp3 - Map marker removal sound
- fog-reveal.mp3 - Fog of war reveal sound
- combat-start.mp3 - Combat begins sound
- combat-end.mp3 - Combat ends sound

## Recommended Sources

You can find royalty-free sound effects at:
- Freesound.org
- Zapsplat.com
- Mixkit.co
- BBC Sound Effects
